A reference implementation (experimental only at present) of a currency accounting application that accesses the [[Open_Transactions]] API.  

Plans for the application include Bitcoin integration to support Bitcoin as one of the currencies used as the verifiable, full-reserve backing in a <span class="plainlinks"><span style="color:black;font-weight:normal; text-decoration:none!important; background:none!important; text-decoration:none;"></span>[Degree](MFA) currency trading system or payment network.

This software was announced on the Bitcoin forum on April 23rd, 2011 (1.1).

